<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
  <head>
    <title>Item List</title>
    <link
      href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Roboto+Condensed:wght@300;400;700&display=swap"
      rel="stylesheet"
    />
    <style>
      body {
        font-family: "Roboto Condensed", sans-serif;
        margin: 0;
        padding: 0;
        display: flex;
        flex-direction: column;
        align-items: center;
        justify-content: center;
        min-height: 100vh;
        background-image: url("https://png.pngtree.com/background/20220718/original/pngtree-love-face-emoji-wallpaper-background-picture-image_1661640.jpg");
        background-size: cover;
        background-position: center;
        background-attachment: fixed;
        background-repeat: no-repeat;
      }

      .container {
        width: 100%;
        max-width: 800px;
        box-sizing: border-box;
        border-radius: 8px;
        display: flex;
        flex-direction: column;
        align-items: center;
        opacity: 1;
      }

      .item {
        border: 1px solid #000000;
        box-sizing: border-box;
        margin: 10px 0;
        border-radius: 4px;
        opacity: 1;
        width: 100%;
      }

      @media (max-width: 600px) {
        .container {
          padding: 10px;
        }

        .item {
          padding: 8px;
          margin: 8px 0;
        }
      }

      .header {
        background-color: #000000;
        width: 100%;
        display: flex;
        justify-content: center;
        align-items: center;
        padding: 15px 0;
        box-sizing: border-box;
      }

      .header img {
        width: 300px;
        height: 150px;
      }

      .centered-text {
        background-color: #000000;
        color: #ffffff;
        /* padding: 10px; */
        text-align: center;
        width: 100%;
        font-size: 20px;
      }
    </style>
  </head>
  <body>
    <div class="header">
      <img
        src="https://res.cloudinary.com/dzhpx2alw/image/upload/v1722616133/Screenshot_2024-08-02_215755_icushj.png"
        alt="Logo"
      />
    </div>

    <div class="centered-text">
      mere babu ne thana thayaaaaaðŸ¥º?
    </div>

    <div
      style="
        width: 100%;
        display: flex;
        justify-content: center; /* Center the container horizontally */
      "
    >
      <div class="container">
        <% if (items && items.length) { %>
          <% items.forEach(function(item) { %>
            <div class="item">
              <%- include('partials/card', { data: item }) %>
            </div>
          <% }); %>
        <% } else { %>
          <p>No items found.</p>
        <% } %>
      </div>
    </div>
  </body>
</html>